manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "doc-storage"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "doc-storage"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["Yggdrasil80 <louisdechorivit@gmail.com>"]
description = "Self-hosted file and document storage service"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = ["doc-storage", "document", "storage", "file", "self-hosted"]
categories = []
license = "GNU General Public License v3.0"
repository = "https://github.com/Yggdrasil80/doc-storage"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
actix-web = "4.2.1"
md-5 = "0.10.4"
redis = "0.21.6"
rusoto_core = "0.48.0"
rusoto_s3 = "0.48.0"
serde_json = "1.0.85"

[dependencies.flate2]
version = "1.0.24"
features = ["zlib"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.144"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.21.1"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.1.2"
features = ["v4", "serde"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "doc_storage"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]
